    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nMany methods in LSP provide workspace-level handling, such as\n* `workspace/(did|will)(Create|Rename|Delete)Files`, related issues: https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/32363, https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/26045\n* `workspace/diagnostic`, tells which files in the workspace have errors.\n\nCurrently, nvim has no opportunity to add this support because there are no built-in features available to use.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nIn addition to providing a basic file browser, more importantly, it can offer a set of APIs that are considered official and can be extended or utilized by plugins.",
